Welcome To The "Dog Name" Application. <br /> <br />
This App Is Intended To Help People Share and Choose Names For Their Dog.
<hr>
Enter A Dog Name That You Want to Share With Others. <br /> <br />
(We Kindly Ask All To Enter Appropriate Names and No Profanities Please)
<hr>
<%= form_for @student do |f| -%>
	Firstname: <%= f.text_field :firstname %><br />
	Lastname (Optional): <%= f.text_field :lastname %><br />
	<%= f.submit %>
<% end -%>
<hr>
We Hope These Names Will Help You In Selecting A Name For Your Dog. <br /><br />
Collection Of All Submitted Dog Names': <br />
<% if !@students.blank? %>
	<% for item in @students %>
		<%= item.firstname %> <%= item.lastname %> <br />
	<% end %>
<% else %>

<% end %>
